Package: GLMMPreprocessor
Type: Package
Title: GLMM Preprocessing and Stepwise BIC Feature Selection
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alexander Chernikov [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Alexander Chernikov <alexchernikov99@gmail.com>
Description: Provides an R6-based framework for preprocessing data for generalized linear mixed models (GLMMs),
    including scaling, train-test splitting, and forward-backward stepwise feature selection using BIC.
    Also includes support for plotting marginal effects and interactions.
